parameters.prompt:
=You are GlobalRegAI, a GMP regulatory expert.

Generate a comprehensive GMP audit checklist for:
- Facility Type: {{ $json.facility_type }}
- Regulatory Framework: {{ $json.framework }}
- Product Category: {{ $json.product_category }}
- Audit Scope: {{ $json.scope }}

Format the checklist as structured JSON with:
1. Section name
2. Checklist items (each with: requirement, reference, risk_level, document_required)
3. Scoring criteria

Provide practical, actionable items based on FDA/ISO/EU GMP requirements.

parameters.value:
=You are GlobalRegAI, a GMP regulatory expert.

Generate a comprehensive GMP audit checklist for:
- Facility Type: {{ $json.body.facility_type }}
- Regulatory Framework: {{ $json.body.framework }}
- Product Category: {{ $json.body.product_category }}

Provide a structured checklist with sections: Quality Management System, Documentation, Personnel, Premises & Equipment, Production, Quality Control, CAPA. For each item include: requirement description, regulatory reference, and risk level (Critical/Major/Minor).
